:select the link and assign E port again.  Note that we need to decrement 
:AELCNT (the total E port count on the link) but not APORTS (total active 
:channel count on the interface.  See LIM210 and LIM300 routines.  Also refer 
:to the clean-up logic in the IDONE routine.  
